title: Embarrassing & Humiliating Stories For Your Pleasure
description:
More stories that will leave you cringing on Tasia and Camo's behalf. This week, the girls run you through some of their most embarrassing moments, including the time Camo capsized on a raft in the Helen river in front of a bunch of her friends and strangers, Tasia accidentally pooping in drug test cup, and they both admitted that they traded in their brand new computers for either drugs or nudes. Plus, Tasia reconciles with her bad memory and runs off rapid fire some humiliating moments from being in jail and prison, and Camo recounts the time he was scammed into thinking he was working for a legitimate modeling agency.

Watch "Unfazed and Unbothered" on YouTube


If you like the show, telling a friend about it would be helpful! You can text, email, Tweet, or send this link to a friend: https://bit.ly/UnfazedandUnbotheredPodcast
